      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://hightower.space/about/quotes/</guid>
      <description>Here are some quotes that are particularly impactful to me:
 &amp;ldquo;Adopt the pace of nature: her secret is patience.&amp;rdquo;
~ Ralph Waldo Emerson
&amp;ldquo;In every walk with nature one receives far more than he seeks.&amp;rdquo;
~ John Muir
&amp;ldquo;Only by going alone in silence, without baggage, can one truly get into the heart of the wilderness. All other travel is mere dust and hotels and baggage and chatter.&amp;rdquo;
~ John Muir</description>
